### List all merchant aliases
GET http://localhost:8080/api/merchant-aliases
Accept: application/json

###

### Get alias by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/merchant-aliases/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Create alias (normalizes "McDonalds 47", "McDonalds 126" etc. to "McDonald's")
POST http://localhost:8080/api/merchant-aliases
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pattern": "(?i)^mcdonalds",
  "canonicalName": "McDonald's"
}

###

### Update alias
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/merchant-aliases/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pattern": "(?i)^mcdonald",
  "canonicalName": "McDonald's"
}

###

### Delete alias (does not revert already-renamed transactions)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/merchant-aliases/1
